    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>The parent <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544542501/AOVs\" rel=\"nofollow\">page describes</a> the AOVs render settings tab. This includes describing the built-in options and how to select what you want.</p><p>However, for many productions you may want to author your own <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661883\" rel=\"nofollow\">LPE</a> using this menu. Below we describe the process.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"651\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmDefaultAOVMenu.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544542604/rfmDefaultAOVMenu.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"858\" data-width=\"497\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544542624\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmDefaultAOVMenu.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544542604\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"4e7be02b-d8ff-4a44-93f6-6f8c08993f6a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmDefaultAOVMenu.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmDefaultAOVMenu.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 1x\"></span><p /><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"6910b1b0-eceb-4d14-9e2f-4a1ee44fd98d\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Be sure to add your own custom AOVs and name them correctly <strong>first</strong> if you intend to add another default or other Display from the presets (the blue menu icon to the right of the Display title contains three presets) otherwise your naming may become incorrect and settings will be forced to be shared if you add them <em>before</em> or <em>during</em> your creation of custom AOVs.</p><p>tl;dr Add default displays from the Display menu (if so desired) after all other displays and channels are added to avoid problems.</p></div></div><p /><p>Notice on the left are the Display Channels, simply called &quot;Channels&quot; here. And on the right are the Display Drivers, referred to here as &quot;Displays&quot;</p><p>Under each section are icons highlighted with a plus sign '+' for creating a new Display Channel or Driver.</p><p>We'll begin with Channels:</p><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Create a new channel by selecting the plus sign</p></li></ol><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"651\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVChannelCreate.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544542604/rfmAOVChannelCreate.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"858\" data-width=\"497\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544542627\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmAOVChannelCreate.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544542604\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"53c4282d-ca10-40d2-94f0-96787be65df8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVChannelCreate.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVChannelCreate.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 1x\"></span><p>2. You can add this channel to the Displays on the right by double-clicking, this will automatically create a new Display Driver. (Or you may use the right-hand plus sign to create a new Display Driver without a Channel) While the new driver is selected you can use the arrow-to-list button (next to the left-hand plus sign) to move the Channel to the highlighted/selected Display Driver you created.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"651\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVDispChannelCreate.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544542604/rfmAOVDispChannelCreate.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"858\" data-width=\"497\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544542630\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmAOVDispChannelCreate.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544542604\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b07b2486-769f-4c64-8416-bc2e43701d53\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVDispChannelCreate.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVDispChannelCreate.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 1x\"></span><p /><p>3. Double-clicking the name will allow you to rename the Display Driver and channels.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"651\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVDispChannelName.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544542604/rfmAOVDispChannelName.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"858\" data-width=\"497\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544542633\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmAOVDispChannelName.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544542604\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"02a0fb3b-63ec-4387-8b04-9000bc6833dd\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVDispChannelName.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVDispChannelName.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 1x\"></span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"bc6a7bdb-8c7e-4518-b203-1074afad6050\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Careful naming will allow the Denoiser to recognize the channels and denoise them. You can find out more about that and the accepted names <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661815\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a> under Layered Filtering (For AOVs). The Denoise utility looks for the correct <em>Channel</em> name to be sure it's using the correct options and filter accordingly.</p></div></div><p>The final example image shows the renaming as well as the LPE to render the Direct Diffuse of the &quot;cup&quot; object. (The Cup object has been correct tagged with an LPE group called &quot;cup&quot;)</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"651\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmCustomAOVCup.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544542604/rfmCustomAOVCup.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"858\" data-width=\"497\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544542636\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmCustomAOVCup.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544542604\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b24206bb-1756-47ee-a83d-099ad6ae4b5d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmCustomAOVCup.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmCustomAOVCup.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"651\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVCupGroup.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=482&amp;height=672\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544542604/rfmAOVCupGroup.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"672\" data-width=\"482\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544542639\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmAOVCupGroup.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544542604\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c0ca30bf-8ea9-4715-8675-44680f98bfd0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVCupGroup.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=482&amp;height=672 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVCupGroup.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586258&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=482&amp;height=672 1x\"></span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"af5b4300-4926-4e07-8473-945e28af0b9e\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Your resulting display drivers will write additional naming information that you did not specify here. The <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544542704/Workspace\" rel=\"nofollow\">Workspace Tab</a> controls what other information is included in your render outputs incliding things like scene name, version, AOV name, camera name, and more.</p></div></div><p>Remember, adding them one at a time without selecting a Display Driver creates multiple outputs, seen here on the left. The other behavior is to select a Display Driver before adding the Channels for a single (or limited) output like the example on the right.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"651\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVMultiEXR.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586445&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544542604/rfmAOVMultiEXR.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586445&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"858\" data-width=\"497\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544542645\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmAOVMultiEXR.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544542604\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3c6f641c-0729-4736-a0ae-9f265e1a465a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVMultiEXR.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586445&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVMultiEXR.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586445&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"651\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVSingleEXR.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586445&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544542604/rfmAOVSingleEXR.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586445&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"858\" data-width=\"497\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544542642\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmAOVSingleEXR.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544542604\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"01f15757-0459-477f-b213-f436d2a70f32\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVSingleEXR.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586445&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544542604/rfmAOVSingleEXR.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431586445&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=858 1x\"></span><p />"
    }
